# Biblio

![Java](https://img.shields.io/badge/Java-17-orange)
![SQLite](https://img.shields.io/badge/Database-SQLite-blue)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-green)

Biblio is a Java-based library management system using SQLite for local data storage.

The project includes:

* Console CLI application
* Swing GUI desktop application
* SQLite database integration
* Object-oriented architecture

---

# вңЁ Features

* рҹ“ҡ Add paper books and ebooks
* рҹ—„пёҸ SQLite database storage
* рҹ”Қ Search books by title or author
* вңҸпёҸ Edit and delete books
* рҹ”„ Check-in / Check-out support
* рҹ’» Swing desktop interface
* вҡЎ CLI version included
* рҹ’ҫ Local database without server

