---

# рҹҡҖ Running the Project

## 1. Clone repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/biblio.git
cd biblio
```

---

# в–¶пёҸ Run CLI Version

```bash
chmod +x run-cli.sh
./run-cli.sh
```

---

# рҹ–ҘпёҸ Run GUI Version

```bash
chmod +x run-gui.sh
./run-gui.sh
```

---

# вҡҷпёҸ Manual Compilation

```bash
javac -cp ".:lib/sqlite-jdbc-3.53.1.0.jar" src/*.java
```

---

# в–¶пёҸ Manual Launch

## CLI

```bash
java -cp ".:src:lib/sqlite-jdbc-3.53.1.0.jar" Main
```

## GUI

```bash
java -cp ".:src:lib/sqlite-jdbc-3.53.1.0.jar" LibraryApp
```

---

# рҹ—„пёҸ Database

The project uses SQLite.

Database file:

```text
data/library.db
```

Tables are created automatically on startup.

---

# рҹ“ҡ Object Model

* `Book` вҖ” base class
* `PaperBook` вҖ” paper book
* `EBook` вҖ” electronic book
* `Library` вҖ” library management
* `DatabaseManager` вҖ” SQLite connection
* `Main` вҖ” CLI entry point
* `LibraryApp` вҖ” Swing GUI application

